To Download:
Hermit Font (~/.local/share/fonts/*)
GVFS

To Centered Windows:
in ~/.config/openbox/lxde-rc.xml
substitute "<applications/>" with:
    <applications>
    <application type="normal">
      <position>
        <x>center</x>
        <y>center</y>
      </position>
    </application>
  </applications>
To mouse follow:
        <followMouse>yes</followMouse>

Clock Format:
%H:%M:%S
Bold Font

Themes:
Breeze
Arc-Dark
Tango Palette
